---
title: Sweet & Spicy Shrimp Lo Mein Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: This saucy noodle stir-fry is packed with crisp sugar snap peas, hearty cabbage and bok choy, and succulent shrimp all tossed in a sauce that’s equal parts sweet, salty, and spicy. A squeeze of fresh lime juice brightens the dish while chopped peanuts, sprinkled on top, ties it all together with a crunchy finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67607e268210a9d71a68d1a9-4f90ba0d.jpeg
